title: What do Russian nationals, analysts make of US-led Ukraine peace talks?
description: While some in Russia believe Ukraine is standing in the way of peace, other analysts say Putin has maximalist ambitions.
content:
From Russias perspective, Ukraines refusal to accept its terms to end the war is the main obstacle to peace.
According to Kyiv and many of its European allies, it is Russian President Vladimir Putin… [+8545 chars]
